# Supabase Services Usage (pointer)

Use this rule only if/when the repository adds Supabase.

Canonical guidance lives in: `@rules/backend/supabase.mdc`.

- Isolate Supabase access in `services/supabase/*`.
- Do not call Supabase directly from components, hooks, utils, or route handlers.
